(51, 1, '2021-05-04 13:19:51', '2021-05-04 12:19:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'m allergic to bee stings. They cause me to, uh, die. When will I learn? The answers to life\'s problems aren\'t at the bottom of a bottle, they\'re on TV! This is the greatest case of false advertising I\'ve seen since I sued the movie \"The Never Ending Story.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your questions have become more redundant and annoying than the last three \"Highlander\" movies. Shoplifting is a victimless crime. Like punching someone in the dark. You know, the one with all the well meaning rules that don\'t work out in real life, uh, Christianity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Uh, no, you got the wrong number. This is 9-12. I prefer a vehicle that doesn\'t hurt Mother Earth. It\'s a go-cart, powered by my own sense of self-satisfaction. Lisa, vampires are make-believe, like elves, gremlins, and Eskimos.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Marge, just about everything\'s a sin. Y\'ever sat down and read this thing? Technically we\'re not supposed to go to the bathroom. Dear Mr. President, There are too many states nowadays. Please, eliminate three. P.S. I am not a crackpot.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-04 13:19:51', '2021-05-04 12:19:51', '', 5, 'http://localhost/?p=51', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
